#

Pork Carnitas Tacos with Spicy Avocado Salsa

$15.99
650 kcal

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Tags:

MexicanPorkTacosCarnitas

Description

Tender pork carnitas wrapped in warm tortillas, topped with a zesty avocado salsa and fresh cilantro.

Ingredients

  • Pork shoulder: 2 lbs
  • Orange juice: 1 cup
  • Lime juice: 1/4 cup
  • Cumin: 1 tsp
  • Chili powder: 1 tsp
  • Oregano: 1 tsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Corn tortillas: 8
  • Avocado: 2
  • Tomato: 1
  • Red onion: 1/2 cup
  • Cilantro: 1/4 cup
